<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash; and M. Roberts (eds.), 2009. <em>Harming
Future Persons: Ethics, Genetics and the Nonidentity Problem</em>,
Dordrecht: Springer.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash; and M. Roberts, 2017. &ldquo;Dividing and
